headline: Boeing Stock Dips. What We Know About the Air India Crash Report That Could Come Tomorrow.
summary: Boeing  stock fell Thursday as investors waited for details from flight data recorders from Air India flight 171, which crashed on June 12, less than a minute after taking off from an airport in Ahmedabad, India.  The Times of India reported Tuesday that a preliminary report had been submitted to officials, citing “top sources.”  Benchmark analyst Josh Sullivan wrote Thursday that he expects a preliminary report to be released on Friday.
